reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easiest Installation Ever. Great Screen Clarity.
reviews.reviewText: The instructions were clear and concise. The tray was perfectly fitted to the size of my phone. The screen protector went on with only two bubbles, which were easily removed. The price was great for the value. I like that it includes two screen protectors. The only issues I had were with the cleaning wipe having a very noxious chemical smell that made me a little dizzy and that the second bubble was not able to be removed with the included squeegee. I had to use the credit card trick where you lift the edge of the screen protector with the card and then push the bubble out by rubbing the screen protector behind it and then put the screen protector back down on the edge. That did the job though and it is perfectly on my screen now with zero bubbles. The clarity of the screen protector is very good. Images look sharper than they did with my previous screen protector from another brand. I’m satisfied with it overall.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Because My iPhone Deserves Fort Knox-Level Protection (with a Dash of Style!)
reviews.reviewText: Ladies, gentlemen, and iPhone enthusiasts, gather 'round, for I have discovered a screen protector that's not just a protector – it's a screen-saving superhero with a flair for fashion! Behold, the Spigen Tempered Glass Screen Protector, the guardian angel of my precious iPhone 14 Pro Max.Now, let's get one thing straight – my iPhone is like my second child (sorry, Siri), and I refuse to let it roam the dangerous world of scratches and smudges without proper protection. Enter the Spigen Tempered Glass, the armor that turns my phone into an invincible knight.Installation? Easier than ordering takeout on a lazy Sunday. It practically applies itself, and it's so forgiving that even if you've never installed a screen protector before, you'll feel like a pro. Case-friendly? You bet! It gets along with my iPhone case like peanut butter and jelly. They're practically besties!But here's the real magic: sensor protection. It's like this screen protector has a PhD in iPhoneology. It guards my sensors with the dedication of a secret service agent, ensuring that Face ID and all my other favorite iPhone tricks work flawlessly. Mission accomplished, 007!Durability? It's like having an Olympic gymnast on my screen. It bends, it flexes, but it never breaks. It laughs in the face of keys, coins, and rogue crumbs, and my phone screen stays as pristine as a freshly baked croissant.Now, let's talk style. This screen protector adds a touch of class to my iPhone that's on par with a tuxedo-wearing penguin. It's crystal clear, it's sleek, and it's so smooth that swiping feels like gliding on a unicorn's back.In conclusion, the Spigen Tempered Glass Screen Protector isn't just a screen protector; it's a guardian angel, a fashion statement, and a tech-savvy guru rolled into one. If you love your iPhone even half as much as I do, this protector is non-negotiable. It's the ultimate wingman for your phone's screen – stylish, reliable, and ready to take on the world. So, go ahead, let your iPhone shine in all its glory while this protector stands guard, because every swipe, tap, and Face ID recognition will feel like pure magic!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 18, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I’ve gone through several different glass screen protectors over the years. I usually pay extra to geek squad at best buy to install my glass screen protectors bc I’m always afraid of screwing it up and having to buy another set. This one by far has been the easiest most straightforward screen protector to install! I’ll be using spigen for all my future devices! It was easy to follow instructions and easy to clear out air bubbles, idk why I can never get all air bubbles out on previous ones I’ve tried! Finally a common sense company product! Loved that it also came with an extra in case you mess up, idk how you could mess up installation but it felt good opening the package knowing there was a “grace” round installation :) The installation tray was awesome it perfectly aligned the glass. After a couple weeks of use, I also love that fingerprints nor smudges stay on the glass; it feels like the glass that’s actually on the iPhone itself, the glass feels nice to the touch. Inevitability my toddler has gotten ahold of my phone and dropped it a few times so it’s seen a few unintentional toddler tests lol :/ So far no cracks! Impressive as my little one is a rough kiddo. I’ve paired the glass screen protector with the spigen clear case, spigen camera lense protectors and the clear magnetic pop socket…idk I’ve been enamored by the clear aesthetics and loving the setup! I never do reviews but had to give a shout-out to this great product! It’s hard to find a good product that actually does what is advertised and this is one of the few.
